        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <para>Our herbarium digitistaion is a three step process; (1) specimens are barcoded and databased to MIDS level 1; (2) specimens are imaged; and (3) specimens are databased to MIDS level 2.</para>
                </description>
            </methodStep>
            <sampling>
                <studyExtent>
                    <description>
                        <para>This resource will cover the full extent of the specimens in Trinity College Dublin herbarium, a global herbarium with specimens dating back to the 18th century.</para>
                    </description>
                </studyExtent>
                <samplingDescription>
                    <para>Our digitistion has begun with the vascular plants of Britain and Ireland, followed by the world vascular plant collection.</para>
                </samplingDescription>
            </sampling>
        </methods>

